Invocation Name: my ideas
des:
Tiny ideas manager to keep track of your ideas, currently you can save one idea, know the last idea saved, list all ideas, and remove it all. 
Please, feel free send to me feedback for improve the skill. 
Thank you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
